  "code": "%%{HealthTech_EMR_Sync}}}%%\nstateDiagram-v2\ntitle: SM-03.01 — Proposal Lifecycle (HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine)\n\n[HealthTech_EMR_Sync] --> DRAFT : ProposalCreated (HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine)\nnote right of DRAFT\n  Authoring & validation:\n  • proposalId assigned\n  • schema/policy checks\nend note\n\nDRAFT --> REVIEW : SubmittedForReview\nnote right of REVIEW\n  Guard reviews (HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault)\n  Can request changes or reject\nend note\n\nREVIEW --> DRAFT : ChangesRequested\nREVIEW --> REJECTED : RejectedAtReview\nREVIEW --> OPEN_FOR_VOTE : ApprovedForVoting (HealthTech_EMR_Sync)\n\nOPEN_FOR_VOTE --> OPEN_FOR_VOTE : VoteCast (HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine)\nOPEN_FOR_VOTE --> TALLYING : VotingClosed\n\nTALLYING --> DECIDED_APPROVED : VoteTallied → Approved (HealthTech_EMR_Sync)\nTALLYING --> DECIDED_REJECTED : VoteTallied → Rejected (HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault)\n\nDECIDED_APPROVED --> EXECUTION : DecisionRecorded (HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine)\nDECIDED_REJECTED --> ARCHIVED : DecisionRecorded (HealthTech_EMR_Sync)\n\nEXECUTION --> EXECUTED : PolicyChanged / GrantApproved / ProjectApproved (HealthTech_EMR_Sync)\nEXECUTION --> EXECUTION_FAILED : ExecutionFailed\n\nEXECUTION_FAILED --> APPEAL : AppealOpened (HealthTech_EMR_Sync)\nEXECUTION_FAILED --> RETRY_EXEC : RetryAuthorized\nRETRY_EXEC --> EXECUTION : ReExecute\n\nEXECUTED --> AUDIT : ExecutionCompleted\nAUDIT --> ARCHIVED : AuditLogged (HealthTech_EMR_Sync)\n\n%% Appeals (HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault)\nOPEN_FOR_VOTE --> APPEAL : AppealOpened (HealthTech_PatientRecords)\nDECIDED_APPROVED --> APPEAL : AppealOpened (HealthTech_PatientRecords)\nDECIDED_REJECTED --> APPEAL : AppealOpened (HealthTech_EMR_Sync)\n\nAPPEAL --> DECIDED_APPROVED : AppealResolved → uphold\nAPPEAL --> DECIDED_REJECTED : AppealResolved → overturn\nAPPEAL --> ARCHIVED : AppealWithdrawn\n\n%% Cancellations\nDRAFT --> CANCELLED : WithdrawnByAuthor\nOPEN_FOR_VOTE --> CANCELLED : CancelledByAuthority\nCANCELLED --> ARCHIVED : Archived\n\n